h1. max

h2. Purpose

Ensures a value does not exceed the given maximum value.

h2. Examples

{code:java}
age(max:new Date())
price(max:999F)
{code}

h2. Description

Sets the maximum value of a class that implements java.lang.Comparable. The same type needs to be used as the property itself. This constraint influences [schema generation|guide:5.7 GORM and Constraints].

Error Code: @className.propertyName.max.exceeded@

